net.sourceforge.waters.model.compiler.graph

Class ModuleGraphCompiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.waters.model.base.DefaultProxyVisitor
      • net.sourceforge.waters.model.module.DefaultModuleProxyVisitor
        • net.sourceforge.waters.model.compiler.graph.ModuleGraphCompiler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.sourceforge.waters.model.analysis.Abortable, ProxyVisitor, ModuleProxyVisitor

    public class ModuleGraphCompiler
extends DefaultModuleProxyVisitor
implements net.sourceforge.waters.model.analysis.Abortable
    The fourth and final pass of the compiler.

    This compiler accepts a ModuleProxy as the input and returns a ProductDESProxy as the output. It assumes that the input module only contains nodes of the type SimpleNodeProxy, and that its edges have neither guards nor actions.

    Author:
    Robi Malik
